/-!
# Chebotarev density theorem

A formalisation of the Chebotarev density theorem in conjugacy-class form
for a finite Galois extension of number fields, following Sharifi,
*Algebraic Number Theory* §7.1–7.2.

This root module currently re-exports `CebotarevDensity.ForMathlib`, which
collects general analytic limit lemmas flagged as candidates for
upstreaming to mathlib; the development modules land here as the
slice-PRs from `development` are merged.
-/
